name: LIBRE EAU DE TOILETTE
description: Because freedom is more relevant now than it ever was. It resonates in a personal, emotional, intimate manner. More than a state of mind, it's a way to live. To feel everything on your skin. To embrace who you are, your emotions, your desires. Burning bright. Feeling right. Smelling marvellous all the while, in the radiant sillage of Libre Eau de Toilette.
